productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Elisha has one of these. She works as a fortune teller and she says it looks floppy.
i use it never again when i'm in my station.

My co-worker Kazuo has one of these. He says it looks transparent.
I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
